<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %> | TechnoVED</title>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #2e1065, #0b0614);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .screen {
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .content {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 500px;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .content img {
      width: 280px;
      max-width: 80%;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
      100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 96px;
      color: #c084fc;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #ddd6fe;
      margin: 15px 0 30px;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7c3aed, #a855f7);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.6);
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    a:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.85);
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 64px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="screen">
    <div class="content">

      <img src="/images/error.jpg" alt="Broken Robot">

      <h1><%= title %></h1>

      <p>
        <%= message %><br>
        Robot tried debugging‚Ä¶ now it‚Äôs crying ü§ñüò≠
      </p>

      <a href="/">Go Home üè†</a>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
